{
  "stem": "1502.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But I'm not going to do it, he said, because when the enemy will come in, he'll make propaganda out of this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Apparently, he was ordered to do it, that's what we found out later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But he disobeyed the order, and he didn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "On the night of September the 3rd, around midnight, they all left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They opened the gates, and the entire caravan-- all the cars, all the trucks, they all left the camp to our disbelief.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Wait a second.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They-- they left the camp, and there were no Germans in the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The Jews got together-- anyway, most of them or maybe all of them-- they all came to our hall, and we organized a service, a religious service.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we prayed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we said, you know, Hallel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "You know, Hallel you only said-- say on big holidays.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "On very important holidays, we say Hallel, which is thanksgiving.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "So we didn't hesitate for one minute that this is the biggest holiday of all the Jewish holidays, and we said Hallel.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And people came that never prayed in their life, everybody was there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "A lot of people cried, it was very emotional.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And after this, we danced.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Went around, all around, all around like a dance at the Jewish wedding.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We were singing and dancing for a long time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Then we went to sleep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "We put a few guys on guard on the outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And in the morning, we woke up very early, very early.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "As soon as the daybreak, we started to move out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I want you to know that we got out of the camp, there was no reception committee outside to-- to receive us, to give us a welcome.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
